pill; eight million pounds of that

00:11:14.780 --> 00:11:16.420
in the united States
in human medicine.

00:11:16.420 --> 00:11:19.950
American Medical Association and
the American Academy of Pediatrics,

00:11:19.950 --> 00:11:22.390
all these different associations
say, "This is too much.

00:11:22.390 --> 00:11:23.690
We need to cut it back.

00:11:23.690 --> 00:11:25.050
We're overusing antibiotics."

00:11:25.050 --> 00:11:26.350
And why do they say that,

00:11:26.350 --> 00:11:29.620
