00:14:50.830 --> 00:14:52.500
to make these animals sick.

00:14:52.500 --> 00:14:54.990
But rather than change
this system --

00:14:54.990 --> 00:15:00.600 position:56%
don't ask me how, maybe
distributing smaller feedlots closer

00:15:00.600 --> 00:15:04.080
to the grazing lands.

00:15:04.080 --> 00:15:07.220
Instead of changing that, we just
give them all antibiotics right

00:15:07.220 --> 00:15:09.400
at that time when we're about
to put them all together

00:15:09.400 --> 00:15:12.590
in those fecal wastelands.

00:15:12.590 --> 00:15:14.800
So that's one production
disease that we're treating.

00:15:14.800 --> 00:15:18.350
Another one is when you switch
these animals that have evolved

00:15:18.350 --> 00:15:21.340
to eat grass, and you switch
them to corn and soybean,

00:15:21.340 --> 00:15:23.370
