either the gut of that animal,

00:16:14.670 --> 00:16:16.800
or the skin of those animals.

00:16:16.800 --> 00:16:19.880
And then those bacteria can then go
on to cause infections in people,

00:16:19.880 --> 00:16:21.730
and we get the little frowny faces.

00:16:21.730 --> 00:16:24.420
And again, the problems
