fewer choices

00:16:27.180 --> 00:16:28.900
for treating those infections,

00:16:28.900 --> 00:16:31.800
and we know that those infections
last longer, and they cost more

00:16:31.800 --> 00:16:36.260
to treat, and they
result in more deaths.

00:16:36.260 --> 00:16:40.930
So I just wanted to underscore
something because, again,

00:16:40.930 --> 00:16:43.320
