antibiotics in the meat

00:16:50.200 --> 00:16:53.470
that we're most concerned
about, it's drug-resistant --

00:16:53.470 --> 00:16:56.470
living infectious,
drug-resistant bacteria

00:16:56.470 --> 00:17:00.820
