00:17:11.980 --> 00:17:14.170
And so when you go to
slaughter those animals,

00:17:14.170 --> 00:17:19.170
you're going to contaminate
the meat with those bacteria.

00:17:19.170 --> 00:17:25.160
Okay; so for years, we -- it turns
