They really control
antibiotics in animals,

00:49:23.950 --> 00:49:26.350
they really control
antibiotics in human medicine,

00:49:26.350 --> 00:49:28.440
and have really good
hygiene in the hospitals,

00:49:28.440 --> 00:49:32.210
